          "content": "I hear you. I know this is really serious and scary for him.\n\nIs he home now? Has he been arrested or anything, or did he just come back home after driving off?\n\nAnd what about the other car - was there any damage that you can see? Did anyone inside get hurt?\n\nI'm here to talk through this with you. Whatever happens next, I know you're trying to help him out right now."
