          "content": "I understand. Let me know what you need help with right now.\n\nIs he home? Has the police or anyone else contacted you guys yet?\n\nIf he's not home, I'd wait until he gets back before trying to talk through everything. He needs time to process this himself and collect his thoughts.\n\nIf someone is already involved - like the other car's owner or police - then yes, you'll want to help him tell the truth in a calm, clear way.\n\nBut first things first - where is he right now?"
